---
title: Bengal Chickpea & Green Bean Curry with Rapid Rice, Lime & Yoghurt
description: Warm, fragrant, and on the table in no time! This veggie-friendly curry is a speedy yet satisfying dish, loaded with protein-packed chickpeas, aromatic spices and tender green veg. Served with fluffy rapid rice and a zingy hit of lime, it’s a bowl full of comfort with a fresh twist!

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67ca8d8425f33d23e0b3dcd9-24cabf99.jpeg
